
The database columns on_state and off_state are the values to publish in order to update the device under control and should not be used to set the value of 'state'.

==========================================================


Extend mySqlClient.py as follows

Create language interpreter:

^clear      Clear results

^exit       Exit client when user disconnects.

Returns:

^ok <count> Succes, count is of number of rows returnrd (0 means none, or irrelevent)

^error


